description.code:
Goodies, samples, background & noises from - THE TELETUBIES, THE BRAIN, ULYSSE 31, A-HA, AAVIKKO, COCK ROCK DISCO, VANESSA PARADIS, EMILIE ET SES AMIS.

Except * (unreleased), materials used for this broadcast come from their original supports.
Recorded in Berlin early spring 2006. .

www.larmeedesbonbons.org/damie/
